{"tid":2069510,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是日晚餐 泡菜國套餐  & 撚廚","createTime":"2020-06-18T12:30:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T08:00:15.000Z","uid":260581,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f90e6deb88f982901065d38321d7a1f24b6420f9","tid":2069510,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:30:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZWTn7h0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZWTn7h0.jpg&h=01fda13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n塊扒係個尾位 我改得唔好<br />\n一半大 一半細<br />\n搞到煎出嚟有半邊是overcook <br />\n<br />\n蘿蔔好酸 醋同水既比例應該接近1:1<br />\n加返少少水落去就啱味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1966b02e60388a8afd216914de070695c1eb6653","tid":2069510,"uid":293632,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:32:32.000Z","msg":"減緊肥 <br />\n見到人食白飯好羨慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1065840299ed50901c68c5e3337eb803ac1402d6","tid":2069510,"uid":260581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:32:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FV4iFE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFV4iFE3.jpg&h=75ff20c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/howduyp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhowduyp.jpg&h=93560daf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我原先見佢話即叫即炸我先入去<br />\n點知落完單先知無茄子 早知唔食<br />\n雞是我揀 蟹餅是日本小姐姐幫我揀的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3945225342d3e05cde81bb1d3c5ad99ecd877322","tid":2069510,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T12:33:16.000Z","msg":"想食牛扒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f91b01a0773